author: Amos Morale III, NOLA.com | The Times-Picayune
title: Lil' Boosie to ESPN: LSU's Les Miles is sometimes 'too timid'
text:
Baton Rouge Rapper Lil Boosie made an appearance on ESPN's "Highly Questionable" and was asked to give his thoughts on LSU football coach Les Miles.
Boosie told the show's host Dan Lebatard and Bomani Jones that he felt the LSU coach can sometimes be "too timid."
He also discuss his jailtime and music on the show.
